 ## Source classes
@@
 | `APPENDIX` | Subordinate Alfred appendix | May hold detail and retrieval support; does not become canonical doctrine merely by existing. |
+| `UPLOAD` | Attached/read source-extension material | May support finalization-source input only where directly read and represented in the finalization plan. |
